3) Loss:
   - Q weighted NSE term computed ONLY over q_mask (availability) AND q_true>eps
   - T MSE computed ONLY over temp availability mask

Everything else (Polars ingestion, dataset windows, evaluation/plots, saving artifacts)
remains consistent with your script.
"""


